    "question": {
        "en": "IF AND ONLY IF parent asks for reason for education and race/ethnicity questions, RA may respond accordingly:\"We are asking this information to assess how well we are doing in reaching all members of society.  It is important that we study children who reflect the diversity of the US and we want to ensure that we get involvement from folks who are often not included in studies, including many minority groups.\" \n\"Estamos pidiendo esta informacion para evaluar que tan bien estamos contactando a todos los miembros de la sociedad. Es importante que estudiemos a ni\u00c3\u00b1os que reflejan la diversidad de los EE. UU. y queremos asegurarnos que participen personas que muchas veces no son incluidas en los estudios, incluyendo muchos grupos minoritarios.\"If there is indication of concern or discomfort in answering the questions about race and/or ethnicity, then say:\"You are free to decline answering this question.\"\n\"Usted es libre de negarse a responder esta pregunta.\""
